Name: script editor

Synonyms: script editor,script window,script palette

Type: glossary

Description:
The window in which you edit <script|scripts>. You can open the script editor by selecting the <object> and clicking on the Script button in the LiveCode Menubar or choosing Development menu<img src="202656"></img>Object Script, by using the contextual-menu shortcut, or by using the edit command.

